      <arrangement id="aspace_57a290e2ddff357f713114aca6407da2">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged in ascending order of numbers assigned to Harvey Cushing's writings in the publication <title>
               <part>A bibliography of the writings of Harvey Cushing; prepared on the occasion of his seventieth birthday April 8, 1939, by the Harvey Cushing society</part>
            </title>. Springfield, Illinois : C.C. Thomas, 1939.</p>
      </arrangement>
